    • com.c77.androidstreamingclient.lib.rtp.H264DataPacket

  • public class H264DataPacket
extends java.lang.Object
    DataPacket wrapper that includes knowledge about the NAL type and the interpretation of the packet's bits according to H.264 specifications.
